import React from 'react'
import { ReactComponent as Alien } from './alien.svg'
import { ReactComponent as Diamond } from './diamond.svg'
import { ReactComponent as Dog } from './dog.svg'
import { ReactComponent as Fire } from './fire.svg'
import { ReactComponent as Hen } from './hen.svg'
import { ReactComponent as Moth } from './moth.svg'
import { ReactComponent as Plant } from './plant.svg'
import { ReactComponent as Skateboard } from './skateboard.svg'
import { ReactComponent as Toast } from './toast.svg'
import { ReactComponent as Tomato } from './tomato.svg'
import { ReactComponent as Tv } from './tv.svg'
import { ReactComponent as Umbrella } from './umbrella.svg'

export const icons = {
  alien: <Alien />,
  diamond: <Diamond />,
  dog: <Dog />,
  fire: <Fire />,
  hen: <Hen />,
  moth: <Moth />,
  plant: <Plant />,
  skateboard: <Skateboard />,
  toast: <Toast />,
  tomato: <Tomato />,
  tv: <Tv />,
  umbrella: <Umbrella />
}
